---

<div class="principal">
  <div class="prin_ctn">
    <img class="star" src="/Testimonial Page/Star_fill.svg" />
    <h1>Reviewers</h1>
    <p class="desc">
      Reviewers is where people can access guidelines, checklists, and other
      tools to assist them in reviewing papers or manuscripts. It provides a
      structured approach to ensure that the review process is thorough,
      efficient, and consistent.
    </p>
    <aside class="checks">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Done_ring_round_fill.svg" />
          <p>Checklist to Review an Academic Paper</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Done_ring_round_fill.svg" />
          <p>Peer Review Checklist</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Done_ring_round_fill.svg" />
          <p>Checklist for Editors, Reviewers, and Authors of SPIE Journals</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </div>
  <div class="cards_ctn">
    <article class="ctn_google">
      <aside>
        <img
          class="logo"
          src="/Testimonial Page/google-testimonial.png"
        />
        <picture>
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Star_fill.svg" />
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Star_fill.svg" />
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Star_fill.svg" />
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Star_fill.svg" />
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Star_fill_gray.svg" />
        </picture>
      </aside>
      <aside>
        <h5>Samantha Lee</h5>
        <p>The checklist ensures that the review process is thorough</p>
      </aside>
    </article>
    <article class="ctn_meta">
      <aside>
        <img class="logo" src="/Testimonial Page/meta-testimonial.png" />
        <picture>
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Star_fill.svg" />
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Star_fill.svg" />
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Star_fill.svg" />
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Star_fill.svg" />
          <img src="/Testimonial Page/Star_fill.svg" />
        </picture>
      </aside>
      <aside>
        <h5>Rachel Patel</h5>
        <p>I highly recommend the Writecream Business Description</p>
      </aside>
    </article>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .principal {
    font-family: "Sora";
    height: 100vh;
    width: auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 30px;
    background-color: #fafaf9;
  }

  p{
    color: #52525A;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .prin_ctn,
  .cards_ctn {
    width: 50%;
    margin: 0 25px;
    max-width: 660px;
  }

  .prin_ctn {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  .prin_ctn .desc {
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .prin_ctn aside ul li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .prin_ctn aside ul li p {
    text-align: justify;
    margin: 0 5px;
  }

  .prin_ctn .checks {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .prin_ctn .star {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
  }

  .cards_ctn {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 0.5fr 1fr 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: 190px 190px;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cards_ctn article {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: #fff;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    max-width: 360px;
    box-shadow: 0px 30px 100px 0px rgba(17, 23, 41, 0.05);
  }

  .cards_ctn aside:first-child {
    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .cards_ctn aside .logo {
    height: 40px;
  }

  .cards_ctn .ctn_google {
    grid-column-start: 2;
    grid-column-end: 6;
    grid-row-start: 1;
    grid-row-end: 2;
  }

  .cards_ctn .ctn_meta {
    grid-column-start: -6;
    grid-column-end: -2;
    grid-row-start: 2;
    grid-row-end: 3;
  }

  .cards_ctn picture {
    display: flex;
  }

  h5 {
    font-weight: 900;
    font-family: "Sora";
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 930px) {
    .cards_ctn article {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .cards_ctn aside .logo {
      height: 30px;
    }

    .cards_ctn p {
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .cards_ctn h5 {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .cards_ctn article {
      justify-content: space-evenly;
    }

    .prin_ctn .desc {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .prin_ctn h1 {
      font-size: 25px;
    }

    .prin_ctn .checks {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 800px) {
    .principal {
      flex-direction: column;
      height: auto;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 80px 30px;
    }

    .prin_ctn,
    .cards_ctn {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .cards_ctn {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.5fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 500px) {
    .cards_ctn {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
